      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To establish the use of ranked choice voting in elections for Representatives in Congress, to require each State with more than one Representative to establish multi-member congressional districts, to require States to conduct congressional redistricting through independent commissions, and for other purposes.</title>
